{"tid":605603,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想問玩滑板嘅師兄會點保護自己","createTime":"2018-03-25T20:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T22:25:43.000Z","uid":84511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"018eb0979a64c788453daa09b763900237d0f3be","tid":605603,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T20:29:24.000Z","msg":"小弟啱啱開咗玩滑板一個星期<br />\n我知玩得預咗跌傷扭傷斷幾條骨<br />\n但成廿幾歲先開始玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自知啲靭帶無玩開嘅咁有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好驚疲勞會令自己更易受傷<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位師兄會點保養自己啲關節<br />\n除咗玩得耐返去冰敷膝頭<br />\n仲有冇其他方法<br />\n同埋邊啲關節特別要保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a69d5a3af4bbbf4bc48069bfc6c32a8d2c5f18","tid":605603,"uid":106169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T22:16:45.000Z","msg":"仆街個時唔好用手撐實地下，由得個人碌落地瀉走d力，不論仆前仆後<br />\n咁樣會冇咁易整傷隻手<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660e59c1cdf65382307703b66d25b6b8fa95b5b0","tid":605603,"uid":12754,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:06:11.000Z","msg":"唔玩"},{"pid":"b10f8b4ae9a02689da2b0a53330a9e2b627d9992","tid":605603,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"弱智 著沙士件衫囉碌柒"},{"pid":"8de2c45a3e152a6282f5cfdcf70372eb30ecda99","tid":605603,"uid":115306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:38:54.000Z","msg":"著長褲"},{"pid":"202c3d3c5bda91d32b88b5d54970b73e68fe8204","tid":605603,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10f8b4ae9a02689da2b0a53330a9e2b627d9992","tid":605603,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"弱智 著沙士件衫囉碌柒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"係咪誤會咗啲咩<br />\n我唔係驚跌傷喎<img src=\"/ass