12ce","tid":605603,"uid":140384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"又怕痕又怕痛 又怕屎彿有條蟲"},{"pid":"fe6b9fca951364ab8b9bb0099cd9351d9c14a3fa","tid":605603,"uid":132790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202c3d3c5bda91d32b88b5d54970b73e68fe8204","tid":605603,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10f8b4ae9a02689da2b0a53330a9e2b627d9992","tid":605603,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"弱智 著沙士件衫囉碌柒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"係咪誤會咗啲咩<br />\n我唔係驚跌傷喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係驚靭帶唔夠力會傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:05:50.000Z","msg":"去開邊度踩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n練吓體能同加強吓啲肌肉<br />\n唔係話要練到六舊出曬嚟<br />\n但係肌肉強啲 會幫你缷走部份嘅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8856a60265a6ddc99305571cb9d0a26e11125db","tid":605603,"uid":159274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:15:39.000Z","msg":"無玩開滑板，不過斷過韌帶。<br />\n跳躍既動作係有機會整傷韌帶。如果想保護韌帶，可以練下大脾舊四頭肌。<br />\n做下d深蹲/squat jump動作。<br />\n不過姿勢要做得岩，如果亂9咁做深蹲/squat jump，反而會愈做愈傷，google下/搵人教啦。"},{"pid":"eaa9125052f9da1254563a4f3e725624003c12a1","tid":605603,"uid":159274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"仲有身體既flexibility好重要。<br />\n平時要拉鬆d筋，增加身體/肌肉既靈活性，冇咁易扭傷。<br />\n同埋最重要係做熱身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d885b7cb74fffb09c6fe0ea2430b19fbf05a8459","tid":605603,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6b9fca951364ab8b9bb0099cd9351d9c14a3fa","tid":605603,"uid":132790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202c3d3c5bda91d32b88b5d54970b73e68fe8204","tid":605603,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b